FLUPS Licensing
============================================

This file includes all licenses that apply within FLUPS (this program) source tree, in particular any that are supposed to be exposed to the end user for credit requirements for instance. 

FLUPS is a Fourier-based Library of Unbounded Poisson Solvers.

